cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.SE 

The paper focuses on AutoML, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). It also deals with the allocation of computation devices to multiple users, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes a new algorithm for multi-device, multi-tenant model selection, which involves system-level design and optimization (cs.SY). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed algorithm on two applications of automatic model selection, which involves software engineering (cs.SE).
